one for my mother.

299
00:15:22,222 --> 00:15:23,855
And I don't even have
to think about it.

300
00:15:23,857 --> 00:15:25,623
I don't have to worry about it.

301
00:15:29,461 --> 00:15:30,962
I spend...

302
