what to do with them,

305
00:15:39,072 --> 00:15:41,339
and I call Lori...

306
00:15:41,341 --> 00:15:42,840
But she...

307
00:15:42,842 --> 00:15:44,309
Well, she doesn't...

308
00:15:44,311 --> 00:15:46,110
She doesn't want my advice
